gJUnit4ClassRunner, which is optional upstream and is exercised by the existing coverage.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No Docker image, environment variable, or system property is required for baseline coverage. Prefer self-contained TestContext, annotation, mock environment, and AOT-hint tests. If testing AOT generation paths, account for Spring's native-image/AOT runtime guard instead of assuming processAheadOfTime is always allowed.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"spring-test contains many optional integrations; tests that intentionally cover MockMvc/mock web, Mockito bean overrides, reactive web support, HtmlUnit/Selenium, TestNG, or JDBC/transaction support may need additional targeted dependencies, but those are not required for baseline meaningful coverage.\",\n    \"The current failing assertion appears to be a Spring 7 behavior/API expectation issue rather than missing Docker or environment setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0500b890c253ba2c016a29236bd9ac819592578b2ad377fdf9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1885, "output": 1047, "cacheRead": 37888, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 40820, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781080922701, "responseId": "resp_0500b890c253ba2c016a29235b5d108195b7eeb72f37deb1c0"}, "toolResults": []}
